<h3 id="linux修改接口IP和DNS"><a href="#linux修改接口IP和DNS" class="headerlink" title="linux修改接口IP和DNS"></a>linux修改接口IP和DNS</h3><p>1.ifconfig 查看接口的名字</p>
<p>2.找到路径<br><code>/etc/sysconfig/network-scripts/</code></p>
