  <entry>
    <title>思科WLC命令</title>
    <url>/2021/06/01/%E6%80%9D%E7%A7%91WLC%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>思科WLC命令</p>
<span id="more"></span>
<h2 id="AP的基本配置命令"><a href="#AP的基本配置命令" class="headerlink" title="AP的基本配置命令"></a>AP的基本配置命令</h2><h3 id="配置AP的IP地址及网关："><a href="#配置AP的IP地址及网关：" class="headerlink" title="配置AP的IP地址及网关："></a>配置AP的IP地址及网关：</h3><p>AP#capwap ap ip add  [IP address]  [netmask]<br>AP#capwap ap ip default-gateway [Gateway Address]       </p>
<h3 id="清除AP的IP地址及网关："><a href="#清除AP的IP地址及网关：" class="headerlink" title="清除AP的IP地址及网关："></a>清除AP的IP地址及网关：</h3><p>clear capwap ap ip address<br>clear capwap ap ip default-gateway </p>
<p>AP#capwap ap erase all</p>
<h3 id="配置AP的WLC控制器地址"><a href="#配置AP的WLC控制器地址" class="headerlink" title="配置AP的WLC控制器地址"></a>配置AP的WLC控制器地址</h3><p>AP#capwap ap primary-base [Controller name] [Controller address]</p>
<p>查看WLC的黑名单<br>(Cisco Controller) &gt;show exclusionlist</p>
<p>添加一个用户MAC到黑名单<br>(Cisco Controller) &gt;config exclusionlist add 00:11:22:33:44:55</p>
<p>从黑名单删除一个用户MAC<br>(Cisco Controller) &gt;config exclusionlist delete 00:11:22:33:44:55</p>
<p>打掉用户无线连接<br>(Cisco Controller) &gt;config client deauthenticate  &lt;MAC addr | IPv4/6 addr | user name&gt;</p>
<h2 id="无线的信号"><a href="#无线的信号" class="headerlink" title="无线的信号"></a>无线的信号</h2><p><a href="https://www.cisco.com/c/en/us/td/docs/wireless/technology/apdeploy/8-0/Cisco_Aironet_3700AP.html">https://www.cisco.com/c/en/us/td/docs/wireless/technology/apdeploy/8-0/Cisco_Aironet_3700AP.html</a></p>
<p>Called-Station-ID: Normally Contains the MAC address of the Access Point and the SSID on which the wireless device is connecting. These 2 fields are separated by a colon. Example: “AA-BB-CC-DD-EE-FF:SSID_NAME”.</p>
<p>Calling-Station-ID: Contains the MAC address of the wireless device. Example: “AA-BB-CC-DD-EE-FF”.</p>
<h2 id="无线证书验证文档"><a href="#无线证书验证文档" class="headerlink" title="无线证书验证文档"></a>无线证书验证文档</h2><p><a href="https://www.cisco.com/c/en/us/support/docs/wireless-mobility/wireless-lan-wlan/213543-configure-eap-tls-flow-with-ise.html">https://www.cisco.com/c/en/us/support/docs/wireless-mobility/wireless-lan-wlan/213543-configure-eap-tls-flow-with-ise.html</a><br><a href="https://www.cisco.com/c/en/us/support/docs/security/identity-services-engine/214975-configure-eap-tls-authentication-with-is.html">https://www.cisco.com/c/en/us/support/docs/security/identity-services-engine/214975-configure-eap-tls-authentication-with-is.html</a>
 </p>
]]></content>
