    <title>思科交换机stack和VSS</title>
    <url>/2021/06/01/%E6%80%9D%E7%A7%91%E4%BA%A4%E6%8D%A2%E6%9C%BAstack%E5%92%8CVSS/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>思科交换机stack和VSS</p>
<span id="more"></span>
<h2 id="配置domain"><a href="#配置domain" class="headerlink" title="配置domain:"></a>配置domain:</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">9500-A#conf t</span><br><span class="line">9500-A(config)#stackwise-virtual</span><br><span class="line">9500-A(config-stackwise-virtual)#domain 1 </span><br><span class="line">9500-A(config-stackwise-virtual)#exit</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="配置virtual-link"><a href="#配置virtual-link" class="headerlink" title="配置virtual-link:"></a>配置virtual-link:</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">9500-A(config)#inter ran ten 1/0/1, ten 1/0/2</span><br><span class="line">9500-A(config-if-range)#stackwise-virtual link 1 </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="配置-dual-detection-link"><a href="#配置-dual-detection-link" class="headerlink" title="配置 dual-detection link"></a>配置 dual-detection link</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">9500-A(config)#int te1/0/3</span><br><span class="line">9500-A(config-if)#stackwise-virtual dual-active-detection</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="配置优先级"><a href="#配置优先级" class="headerlink" title="配置优先级"></a>配置优先级</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">9500-A#switch 1 priority 15</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
